`,a.jsxs(e.p,{children:["There are a bunch of different IDEs on the market, and in general you should be able to use any of these that you like and are comfortable with. If you don't have a personal preference, we recommend trying ",a.jsx(e.a,{href:"https://code.visualstudio.com",children:"Visual Studio Code"})," - it is quite excellent and comes with a variety of tools to make your development experience seamless. And it's free!"]}),`
